"type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["<em>Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.</em>","The Riccar Radiance Premium is a <a href=\"/best-deep-vacuum-cleaners\">deep-cleaning vacuum</a> with an innovative motor system. This upscale vacuum, like all Riccar models, is manufactured in the United States. The Radiance Premium has unique features and convenient onboard tools to help you clean many surfaces in your home. ","Riccar vacuums have two distinct motors that work in series to create maximum air flow to both the floor head and the tools. Most vacuums have a motor that creates either strong floor suction or strong tool suction. The Tandem Air System, which is what Riccar calls their two motors, gets powerful suction to all your surfaces. This is a high quality vacuum cleaner, but if you need something with a more reasonable price, consider the <a href=\"/shark-navigator-lift-away-pro-review\">Shark Navigator Lift-Away Pro</a>. ","The Riccar Radiance premium has helpful features to make your vacuuming as simple as possible. LED headlights reveal dirt and particles that you might otherwise miss while vacuuming the floor. There are convenient onboard tools included with your Riccar to assist in cleaning upholstery and dusting in hard-to-reach places. Indicator lights let you know when to change your bag or replace the filter.","This model has a dirt-sensing illumination on the cleaning head to show you where deeply embedded dirt is on your carpet. Boasting a completely sealed system and a HEPA filter, the Riccar Radiance premium traps particles up to 0.3 microns in size. This keeps dust and allergens out of the air as you vacuum.  The Radiance Premium uses bags to contain the dirt you vacuum.","The Riccar Radiance Premium comes with a five-year warranty. On the Riccar website, you are able to submit a question or concern via email. There is also a toll-free number you can call if you need to speak with a service representative. Only Riccar dealers sell the replacement bags and filters, and there&#39;s a search feature so you can locate the closest dealer to you.","The Riccar Radiance Premium is more expensive than many other vacuums, but the high-end features give your carpeting a thorough vacuuming. With a comprehensive online help center and a five-year warranty, this vacuum is a good investment in the cleanliness of your carpets."]},"id":"6c02111f-d33e-43eb-b395-daa0386d4a82","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_60007","url":"/riccar-radiance-premium-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"angie-parkinson","url":"/author/angie-parkinson","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Angie Parkinson","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"4Pu3Dbh8P3CR8CNSJRVPZP","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-07-18T20:28:00Z","datePublished":"2014-07-18T20:28:00Z","name":"Riccar Radiance Premium","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued.","language":"en","dateModified":"2014-07-18T20:28:00Z","id":"daTkVYMajm8CaVepAm22Ze","meta":{"title":"Riccar Radiance Premium Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"The Riccar Radiance Premium is deep vacuum cleaner which operates with innovative technology to clean your floors. Find out more about this deep vacuum cleaner here."},"products":[{"slug":"riccar-radiance-premium","url":"/product/riccar-radiance-premium","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T18:50:58Z","name":"Riccar Radiance Premium","dateModified":"2019-04-16T18:50:58Z","id":"o3xUodEVVNMNTSNX2ujP3X","dateImported":"2019-04